race.comment: STRUCK GOLD (3) peaks off a nose defeat in a 70 improving again. Third-up now and Todd rides today in a key jockey switch. He can go one better. DEVILS DELIGHT (1) found Boldinho much too good in much tougher 42 days ago but covered the others. His form leading into that stacks up and he will use the inside gate. A chance if presented on song. PEEL THE STICKERS (4) resumes and has transferred from a smart Victorian yard. May finds this a bit short but he has plenty of ability and the betting will be key. PHAROAH MAGIC (2) will find this more suitable but would need to find his best to be winning.
